Installation available for Ubuntu 23.10
-----------------------------------------------------------------
# remove standard package if present
# sudo apt remove shutter
setfacl -m u:_apt:rx . 
wget https://github.com/mvivarelli/shutter-on-wayland/raw/master/shutter-on-wayland_0.99.4-6_all.deb
sudo apt -f install ./shutter-on-wayland_0.99.4-6_all.deb 
# sometines the first run hungs, this is fixed by a restart

Shutter on Wayland Motivation
-----------------------------
Hi guys, My Name is Dominique, I want to improve the quality of the shutter wayland from 
mvivarelli git repos, any help is much appreciated. 
The modification from William Repo are already in this repo too.
